CatDescriptText: The entire flyer Tom Twiss is holding reads, " Stop State Police Now !!!, mass rally Thursday 8pm, Bethesda U.P. Church, 7220 Bennett St., Hear The Parent's Side, Hear The Victims Side, Hear The Truth! (see reverse side), Citizens Opposed to a Police State (COPS)".
